Class StandardRelations

java.lang.Object
io.wcm.caravan.rhyme.api.relations.StandardRelations
public final class StandardRelations extends Object
Constants for some standard link relations used in Related annotations.

    • CURIES

      public static final String CURIES
      A reserved link relation which you can use to hint at the location of resource documentation. There can be multiple links in the 'curies' section. They come with a 'name' and a templated 'href' which must contain the {rel} placeholder. To retrieve documentation about the latest-posts resource, the client will expand the associated CURIE link with the actual link's 'rel'
      See Also:
      • draft-kelly-json-hal-08
